* Ancillary files for R3D package - Optional components

f plugin/r3d_fortran.f90
f plugin/r3d_plugin.c
f plugin/Makefile
f plugin/stplugin.h
f test/test_r3d.do
f test/test_plugin.do
f install_r3d.do

* These files are not required for basic operation but provide:
* - Source code for building the plugin (plugin/ directory)
* - Test scripts (test/ directory)  
* - Alternative installation method (install_r3d.do)